<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
      .header { background-color: #ff9800; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: white; }
      .content { padding: 20px; background-color: #ffffff; }
      .book-info { background-color: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; }
      .urgent { color: #d32f2f; font-weight: bold; }
      .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>⚠️ Book Due Today!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <%= @reader.full_name %>,</p>
        <p class="urgent">This is an urgent reminder that the following book is due TODAY:</p>
        <div class="book-info">
          <h3><%= @book.title %></h3>
          <p><strong>Author:</strong> <%= @book.author %></p>
          <p><strong>Serial Number:</strong> <%= @book.serial_number %></p>
          <p><strong>Borrowed on:</strong> <%= @borrowing.borrowed_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
          <p><strong>Due date:</strong> <%= @due_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %> (Today)</p>
        </div>
        <p><strong>Please return the book today to avoid late fees.</strong></p>
        <p>If you need to extend your borrowing period, please contact the library as soon as possible.</p>
        <p>Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message from the Library System</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
